plicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2686:"<h2>We&#8217;ve made some big changes to our website over the past year, but we&#8217;re not done yet ‚Äì and we need your help.</h2>
<p>Since joining the WPMU DEV team as UX Lead Designer last year, I&#8217;ve been working to improve our website and products so they&#8217;re awesome for folks like you to use.</p>
<p>With that in mind, we&#8217;re re-thinking the user experience of our blog and I&#8217;m keen to hear about how you use it. What do you think of the fonts and colors? Do you find the blog easy to read and navigate? What suggestions to you have to improve usability?</p>
<p><span id="more-151166"></span></p>
<p>If you&#8217;ve got a minute handy, fill in the five-question survey below and let me know what you think. Your feedback will directly influence the changes we make.</p>
<p>Thanks for helping us out!</p>
