<h3>Smush Your Images With WP Smush</h3>
<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-smushit/">WP Smush</a> is an excellent image compression solution for optimizing server space and improving your site&#8217;s performance.</p>
<p>In this post, we covered the plugin&#8217;s full functionality and you should now be in a good position to take things further yourself.</p>
<p>WP Smush is a great place to start if you want to quickly and easily set up image optimization on your site, and¬†<a href="https://premium.wpmudev.org/project/wp-smush-pro/">WP Smush Pro</a> is an upgrade when you want to take your compression game to the next level.</p>
